00502 template <typename T>
00503 struct Interpolator
00504 {
00505     // ------------------------------------------------------------------
00511     void operator () (T& out,const T& a, const T& b, ai_real d) const {
00512         out = a + (b-a)*d;
00513     }
00514 }; // ! Interpolator <T>

00518 template <>

00521         const aiQuaternion& b, ai_real d) const
00522     {
00523         aiQuaternion::Interpolate(out,a,b,d);

00527 template <>
00528 struct Interpolator <unsigned int>  {
00529     void operator () (unsigned int& out,unsigned int a,
00530         unsigned int b, ai_real d) const
00531     {
00532         out = d>0.5f ? b : a;
00533     }
00534 }; // ! Interpolator <aiQuaternion>
